      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOVE IT GEORGIA (2) has a strong record this trip with six wins and six placings from 18 starts. Placed last time (20.01) at Capalaba in a Grade 3/4, finishing third and beaten 0.8 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. BLUE LAKODA (5) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last six runs. Last time finished 2nd on February 24 over 352m at this track behind Boom Town beaten 5.5 lengths (19.59) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Expected to be in this for a long way. REDEEMER'S WAY (8) was below best last time finishing sixth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. GOLDSTAR ANNIE (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
